title: How to Paint: Orruk Warclans Zoggrok Anvilsmasha (and Klonk)
description:
Zoggrok hammers the power of Gorkamorka into orruk weapons, accompanied by his rockbrow squig companion, Klonk! 

In this video we'll show you how to quickly paint your Zoggrok Anvilsmasha to be Battle Ready, then we'll be adding a few extra details to take him to the next level with ease. 

If you're new to painting - check out our Citadel Colour Painting Essentials videos to learn all about it: http://warhammer.me/3Vkojs6
